    "content": "<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>P vs NP - The Complexity of Computation</title>\n<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Code&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@500&display=swap');\n\n  /* Root colors */\n  :root {\n    --color-bg: #121318;\n    --color-dark-bg: #0d0e13;\n    --color-primary: #ff6a3d;\n    --color-secondary: #4ad5a9;\n    --color-accent: #fdc830;\n    --color-text-main: #e1e1e6;\n    --color-text-secondary: #a2a2b8;\n    --color-shadow: rgba(255, 106, 61, 0.3);\n    --color-shadow-secondary: rgba(74, 213, 169, 0.25);\n    --gradient-pvnp: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6a3d 0%, #fdc830 50%, #4ad5a9 100%);\n  }\n\n  /* Reset and base */\n  * {\n    margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box;\n  }\n  html, body {\n    height: 100%;\n    background: var(--color-bg);\n    color: var(--color-text-main);\n    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;\n    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;\n    overflow-x: hidden;\n  }\n\n  /* Container */\n  .container {\n    max-width: 1100px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    min-height: 100vh;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n  }\n\n  /* Header */\n  header {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  header h1 {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 3.9rem;\n    background: var(--gradient-pvnp);\n    background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    color: transparent;\n    letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px var(--color-primary));\n    transition: filter 0.5s ease;\n  }\n  header h1:hover {\n    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 14px var(--color-accent));\n    cursor: default;\n  }\n  header p.subtitle {\n    font-size: 1.3rem;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    margin-top: 0.6rem;\n    letter-spacing: 0.05em;\n    font-style: italic;\n  }\n\n  /* Main content: split layout */\n  main {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 3rem;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n\n  /* Visual Panels */\n  .panel {\n    background: var(--color-dark-bg);\n    border-radius: 1.2rem;\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 20px var(--color-shadow),\n      inset 0 0 15px #0009;\n    flex: 1 1 320px;\n    min-width: 300px;\n    max-width: 520px;\n    padding: 2.2rem 2.6rem 3rem;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: visible;\n    transition: box-shadow 0.6s ease;\n  }\n  .panel:hover {\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 30px var(--color-shadow-secondary),\n      inset 0 0 30px #000f;\n  }\n\n  /* Panel Titles */\n  .panel h2 {\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--color-accent);\n    font-size: 2.4rem;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  .panel p.description {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 460px;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n    user-select: text;\n  }\n\n  /* Circles Animation container */\n  .circles {\n    position: relative;\n    width: 320px;\n    height: 320px;\n  }\n\n  /* Circles base style */\n  .circle {\n    position: absolute;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    border: 3.4px solid var(--color-accent);\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 12px var(--color-accent),\n      inset 0 0 8px var(--color-accent);\n    opacity: 0.23;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.7, 0, 0.3, 1);\n  }\n\n  /* Circles for P panel (orange-red) */\n  .panel.p .circle {\n    border-color: #ff6a3d;\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 16px #ff6a3d,\n      inset 0 0 12px #ff6a3d;\n    opacity: 0.46;\n  }\n  .panel.p .circle.small {\n    width: 70px;\n    height: 70px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -35px;\n    margin-top: -35px;\n    animation: rotateClockwise 42s linear infinite;\n  }\n  .panel.p .circle.medium {\n    width: 140px;\n    height: 140px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -70px;\n    margin-top: -70px;\n    animation: rotateCounter 72s linear infinite;\n  }\n  .panel.p .circle.large {\n    width: 230px;\n    height: 230px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -115px;\n    margin-top: -115px;\n    animation: rotateClockwise 95s linear infinite;\n  }\n\n  /* Circles for NP panel (green-cyan) */\n  .panel.np .circle {\n    border-color: #4ad5a9;\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 16px #4ad5a9,\n      inset 0 0 10px #4ad5a9;\n    opacity: 0.38;\n  }\n  .panel.np .circle.small {\n    width: 80px;\n    height: 80px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -40px;\n    margin-top: -40px;\n    animation: rotateCounter 38s linear infinite;\n  }\n  .panel.np .circle.medium {\n    width: 150px;\n    height: 150px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -75px;\n    margin-top: -75px;\n    animation: rotateClockwise 68s linear infinite;\n  }\n  .panel.np .circle.large {\n    width: 220px;\n    height: 220px;\n    top: 50%;\n    left: 50%;\n    margin-left: -110px;\n    margin-top: -110px;\n    animation: rotateCounter 90s linear infinite;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes rotateClockwise {\n    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n  }\n  @keyframes rotateCounter {\n    from { transform: rotate(360deg); }\n    to { transform: rotate(0deg); }\n  }\n\n  /* Venn Diagram container */\n  .venn-container {\n    position: relative;\n    margin: 3.5rem auto 0;\n    width: 460px;\n    height: 340px;\n  }\n  svg.venn {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n\n  /* Venn Diagram circles: P and NP sets */\n  .venn-circle.p-set {\n    fill: url(#gradientP);\n    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 9px #ff6a3d88);\n    transition: fill 0.6s ease;\n  }\n  .venn-circle.np-set {\n    fill: url(#gradientNP);\n    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 9px #4ad5a988);\n    transition: fill 0.6s ease;\n  }\n  .venn-overlap {\n    fill: url(#gradientIntersect);\n    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px #fdc830bb);\n    transition: fill 0.6s ease;\n  }\n\n  /* Labels inside venn diagram */\n  .venn-label {\n    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    fill: var(--color-text-main);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    font-size: 1.22rem;\n    pointer-events: none;\n    user-select: none;\n    text-shadow:\n      0 0 9px #0009,\n      0 0 2px #0008;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n  }\n\n  /* Text description below venn diagram */\n  .caption {\n    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    max-width: 460px;\n    margin: 1.4rem auto 0;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    text-align: center;\n    user-select: text;\n  }\n\n  /* Explanation text */\n  .explanation {\n    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #151620, #0e0f15);\n    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;\n    border-radius: 1rem;\n    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 1.1rem;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    max-width: 720px;\n    margin: 3rem auto 1rem;\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 22px #fdc83035,\n      inset 0 0 12px #fdc83022;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n\n  /* Bottom controls container */\n  .controls {\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-top: 3rem;\n  }\n  .controls button {\n    background: none;\n    color: var(--color-accent);\n    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    font-size: 1rem;\n    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;\n    border-radius: 2rem;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    transition:\n      background-color 0.4s ease,\n      color 0.4s ease,\n      box-shadow 0.4s ease;\n    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-accent);\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  .controls button:hover,\n  .controls button:focus {\n    background-color: var(--color-accent);\n    color: var(--color-bg);\n    box-shadow:\n      0 0 22px var(--color-accent),\n      0 0 32px var(--color-accent);\n    outline: none;\n  }\n  .controls button:active {\n    transform: scale(0.95);\n  }\n\n  /* Footer */\n  footer {\n    text-align: center;\n    font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n\n  /* Tooltip style for explanation highlight */\n  .tooltip-highlight {\n    cursor: help;\n    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--color-accent);\n    position: relative;\n    color: var(--color-accent);\n  }\n  .tooltip-highlight:hover::after {\n    content: attr(data-tooltip);\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 110%;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n    background: var(--color-accent);\n    color: var(--color-bg);\n    padding: 6px 14px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n    border-radius: 0.5rem;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    pointer-events: none;\n    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--color-accent);\n    opacity: 1;\n    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n    z-index: 10;\n  }\n  .tooltip-highlight::after {\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n    pointer-events: none;\n  }\n\n  /* Scrollbar styled for dark theme */\n  ::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    width: 9px;\n  }\n  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {\n    background: #111217;\n  }\n  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n    background: var(--color-accent);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n  }\n  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {\n    background: var(--color-primary);\n  }\n\n  /* Responsive fonts */\n  @media (max-width: 600px) {\n    header h1 {\n      font-size: 2.8rem;\n    }\n    main {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n    .panel {\n      max-width: 100%;\n      width: 90vw;\n    }\n    .venn-container {\n      width: 90vw;\n      height: auto;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\" role=\"main\" aria-label=\"P versus NP Visualization\">\n    <header>\n      <h1>P vs NP</h1>\n      <p class=\"subtitle\">The great unsolved problem in computational complexity</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n      <section class=\"panel p\" aria-labelledby=\"p-title\" aria-describedby=\"p-desc\">\n        <h2 id=\"p-title\">Class <span style=\"color:#ff6a3d;\">P</span></h2>\n        <p class=\"description\" id=\"p-desc\">\n          Problems solvable quickly – formally <span class=\"tooltip-highlight\" data-tooltip=\"Polynomial Time: time bounded by a polynomial function of input size.\">in polynomial time</span> – by a deterministic computer.\n          Examples: sorting, shortest paths, and simple arithmetic.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"circles\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <div class=\"circle large\"></div>\n          <div class=\"circle medium\"></div>\n          <div class=\"circle small\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"panel np\" aria-labelledby=\"np-title\" aria-describedby=\"np-desc\">\n        <h2 id=\"np-title\">Class <span style=\"color:#4ad5a9;\">NP</span></h2>\n        <p class=\"description\" id=\"np-desc\">\n          Problems verifiable quickly (in polynomial time) if a solution is given, but might <span class=\"tooltip-highlight\" data-tooltip=\"It is not yet known if all NP problems can also be solved quickly (P = NP) or not (P ≠ NP).\">not be solvable quickly</span>.\n          Examples: Boolean satisfiability, traveling salesman, and graph coloring.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"circles\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n          <div class=\"circle large\"></div>\n          <div class=\"circle medium\"></div>\n          <div class=\"circle small\"></div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <section class=\"venn-container\" aria-label=\"Venn diagram illustrating relationship between P and NP\">\n      <svg class=\"venn\" viewBox=\"0 0 440 320\" role=\"img\" aria-labelledby=\"venn-title venn-desc\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" aria-hidden=\"false\" focusable=\"false\">\n        <defs>\n          <linearGradient id=\"gradientP\" x1=\"0%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"100%\">\n            <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#ff6a3dcc\" />\n            <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#fdc830cc\" />\n          </linearGradient>\n          <linearGradient id=\"gradientNP\" x1=\"100%\" y1=\"0%\" x2=\"0%\" y2=\"100%\">\n            <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#4ad5a9cc\" />\n            <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#fdc830cc\" />\n          </linearGradient>\n          <radialGradient id=\"gradientIntersect\" cx=\"50%\" cy=\"50%\" r=\"60%\">\n            <stop offset=\"0%\" stop-color=\"#fdc830cc\" />\n            <stop offset=\"100%\" stop-color=\"#fdc83099\" />\n          </radialGradient>\n          <filter id=\"glow\" x=\"-50%\" y=\"-50%\" width=\"200%\" height=\"200%\" color-interpolation-filters=\"sRGB\">\n            <feDropShadow dx=\"0\" dy=\"0\" stdDeviation=\"4\" flood-color=\"#fdc830\" flood-opacity=\"0.8\"/>\n          </filter>\n        </defs>\n\n        <title id=\"venn-title\">P vs NP Venn Diagram</title>\n        <desc id=\"venn-desc\">\n          This diagram shows two overlapping circles representing the classes P and NP.\n          The overlap area is where P equals NP — a question that remains unsolved in computer science.\n        </desc>\n\n        <!-- P circle -->\n        <circle class=\"venn-circle p-set\" cx=\"150\" cy=\"160\" r=\"110\" filter=\"url(#glow)\" />\n        <text class=\"venn-label\" x=\"150\" y=\"160\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#ff6a3d\" font-weight=\"900\" font-size=\"4rem\" style=\"filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px #ff6a3d);\">P</text>\n\n        <!-- NP circle -->\n        <circle class=\"venn-circle np-set\" cx=\"290\" cy=\"160\" r=\"110\" filter=\"url(#glow)\" />\n        <text class=\"venn-label\" x=\"290\" y=\"160\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#4ad5a9\" font-weight=\"900\" font-size=\"4rem\" style=\"filter: drop-shadow(0 0 6px #4ad5a9);\">NP</text>\n\n        <!-- Intersection shape -->\n        <path class=\"venn-overlap\" d=\"M245 50 A110 110 0 0 1 335 160 A110 110 0 0 1 245 270 A110 110 0 0 1 155 160 A110 110 0 0 1 245 50 Z\" />\n        <text class=\"venn-label\" x=\"240\" y=\"160\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#fdc830\" font-weight=\"700\" font-size=\"1.4rem\" style=\"text-shadow: 0 0 8px #fdc830;\">P = NP?</text>\n      </svg>\n      <p class=\"caption\">\n        The <strong>P</strong> set contains problems solvable fast, the <strong>NP</strong> set those verifiable fast.\n        Their overlap indicates problems quickly solvable <em>and</em> verifiable. Whether these are exactly the same is the <em>millennium question</em>.\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"explanation\" aria-label=\"Detailed explanation of P versus NP problem\">\n      <p>\n        At the heart of <span class=\"tooltip-highlight\" data-tooltip=\"Computational complexity studies how resources like time scale with input sizes.\">computational complexity</span> lies the question:\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-accent); margin: 0.3rem 0 1.5rem 0;\">\n        <q>Can every problem with quickly verifiable solutions also be solved quickly?</q>\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        Class <strong>P</strong> contains problems for which a deterministic algorithm can find solutions in reasonable (polynomial) time.\n        Class <strong>NP</strong> contains problems where a given solution can be verified in polynomial time.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        All problems in <em>P</em> are in <em>NP</em> (since verification can’t be harder than solving), \n        but whether <em>P = NP</em> or <em>P ≠ NP</em> remains <span class=\"tooltip-highlight\" data-tooltip=\"One of the seven Millennium Prize Problems with a $1 million reward for a correct proof by Clay Mathematics Institute.\">unproven and famously elusive</span>.\n      </p>\n      <p>\n        If <strong>P=NP</strong>, it would revolutionize fields like cryptography and optimization — many currently \"hard\" problems would suddenly become tractable.\n        If <strong>P≠NP</strong>, such problems remain inherently complex, preserving existing assumptions about computational difficulty.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-secondary)\">\n        This elegant visualization captures the essence of the question through harmonious colors, geometric harmony, and subtle motion, inviting quiet reflection on this profound theoretical frontier.\n      </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"controls\" aria-label=\"Control buttons\">\n      <button id=\"toggleTheme\" aria-pressed=\"false\" aria-label=\"Toggle color theme\">Toggle Dark / Light Theme</button>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n      © 2024 • Design for P vs NP visualization • Created by ChatGPT\n    </footer>\n  </div>\n\n<script>\n  // Theme toggle: Dark / Light\n  (function() {\n    const btn = document.getElementById('toggleTheme');\n    let dark = true;\n    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {\n      dark = !dark;\n      if (dark) {\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-bg', '#121318');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-dark-bg', '#0d0e13');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-text-main', '#e1e1e6');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-text-secondary', '#a2a2b8');\n        btn.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'false');\n        btn.textContent = 'Toggle Dark / Light Theme';\n        document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#121318';\n      } else {\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-bg', '#f5f5f7');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-dark-bg', '#dfe2ea');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-text-main', '#151518');\n        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--color-text-secondary', '#4a4e69');\n        btn.setAttribute('aria-pressed', 'true');\n        btn.textContent = 'Toggle Dark / Light Theme';\n        document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#f5f5f7';\n      }\n    });\n  })();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
